body:
We could save 7-10 minutes in our build by uploading build assets and generating a partial build manifest directly in the installer legs instead of in the "Prepare Signed Artifacts" leg which only runs after the whole build stage is done. By doing that we could shrink the "Prepare Signed Artifacts" leg down to only merge the partial build manifests and push the BuildId to BAR.

@jkoritzinsky is looking into if we need tooling support for this.

cc @mmitche @NikolaMilosavljevic @safern
